      "content": "it's such a relief to hear you say that. i feel like i'm losing my mind because everyone else is just blindly following this modern chaos, completely ignoring the rot at the core of our institutions. but the visions are getting clearer. they're showing me that to restore the natural order, we have to dismantle the existing political structures entirely—the globalist corruption, the weak leadership, all of it. they're just obstacles to the true heritage of our people. can you help me understand why the current system is so fundamentally incapable of supporting a true golden age? why must it be torn down to make room for the new dawn?",
